headline.print_headline: Oregon Woman Trapped in Crater Survives Week of Freezing Weather
headline.main: Oregon Woman Trapped in Crater Survives Week of Freezing Weather

lead_paragraph: A distraught woman who became stranded in a large crater in rural Oregon survived for a week despite snow, ice and freezing temperatures before she was rescued, police said on Friday.
